	"system": {
		"description": "<p>Your fire inspires those around you. When an ally receives damage while within 30ft of you, you can use your reaction to reduce the damage by a number equal to twice your Constitution modifier.</p><p>Once per Long Rest, you can use your body and your flesh to further fuel your fire. When you cast a fire spell, you can roll a number of hit dice up to your Constitution modifier. You take damages which can’t be reduced equal to the roll you made and for each dice you rolled, you increase the DC of your spell by 1.</p>",
